recipeInstructions.text: Whisk the ground almonds, parmesan, garlic powder and oregano together in a shallow dish.
Beat the egg in a medium bowl and dip each zucchini fry in then coat in the almond mix. Place each fry on a lined baking sheet.
Heat the air fryer to 200Â°C and cook the fries in a single layer (working in batches) for 10-12 minutes until golden and crispy, turning halfway through.
